title: Garbage Strike the Musical
description: A musical based on the best-selling book. The trash is piling up in the streets as garbage workers go on strike.
quote: We’re on strike, we’re on strike. We can do anything that we like.
altHero: garbage works on strike (they are rats wearing orange caps)
alt2: rat worker next to a giant pile of trash
alt3: rat workers dancing with strike signs and top hats
alt4: rat workers wearing tutus, dancing in the dirty streets
